<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pagamento - Modo Escuro</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
            background-color: #121212;
            color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 90%;
            background-color: #1c1c1e;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .pix-code {
            background-color: #242426;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-top: 16px;
            word-wrap: break-word;
            word-break: break-all;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            color: #a1a1a6;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #1d9bf0;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="title">Pagamento via PIX</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Escaneie o código abaixo ou copie para realizar o pagamento:</p>
        <img src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1306809356209356853/1321225177551339561/Screenshot_20241224_181530_InterCo.jpg?ex=676c7655&is=676b24d5&hm=a3f36e2a8f93f6cf3a5188bac671f33d9c1112f830462dc8ea1ccff680bb6edd" alt="QR Code do PIX">
        <div class="pix-code">
            00020101021126580014br.gov.bcb.pix0136de7d5814-b9a3-4357-9232-6d227390718b5204000053039865802BR5915JOAO M B VIEIRA6009SAO PAULO62070503***6304D938
        </div>
        <p class="subtitle">Para dúvidas, <a href="#">entre em contato</a>.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
